snippet: The world champion Dafne Schippers edged the Olympic champion Allyson Felix to win the 200 meters at the Diamond League meeting in Brussels.
lead_paragraph: The world champion Dafne Schippers edged the Olympic champion Allyson Felix to win the 200 meters at the Diamond League meeting in Brussels.

headline.main: Felix Loses by a Tenth in 200
headline.print_headline: Felix Loses by Tenth of a Second
